# scripts/lib/ is a TRACKED source directory (canonical-deploy scaling
# enforcement, S308). The bare `lib/` pattern above catches it as a
# Python build-artifact convention; these negations restore tracking
# for source files only. Bytecode and other generated artifacts under
# scripts/lib/ remain ignored.
